      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Quackgrass (Chiendent in French) is subjective. A bad weed is something that grows where you don't want it to. And what's a weed to one person may not be a weed to another, and what's a weed somewhere may not be a weed somewhere else...it’s complicated! Megan’s show revolves around this notion, ..."
