    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Justin Guitard"
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Justin Guitard"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/inLanguage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": ""
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Ever since he was a little boy, people have been asking him: When are you going to do a comedy show? Well, here it is.\r\nDon't miss your chance to see for yourself whether Justin should have listened to himself and decide he wasn't a comedian after all, or whether the audience was right and he has been wasting his true talent since the beginning of his career.\r\nGaspiller du Talent is the very first one-man show by Justin Guitard, a multidisciplinary artist who will make you laugh and entertain you with his anecdotes in a rapid-fire barrage of comedy, “stepettes” and surprises.\r\n\r\nPerformance in French\r\n "
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "On lui demande depuis qu’il est tout petit : C’est pour quand, le spectacle d’humour? Eh bien, le voilà.\r\nNe manquez pas votre chance de constater par vous-même si Justin aurait dû continuer de s’écouter et se dire qu’il n’est pas un humoriste, ou si, finalement, le public avait raison et qu’il gaspille son vrai talent depuis le début de sa carrière.\r\nGaspiller du talent, c’est le tout premier one-man show de Justin Guitard, un artiste pluridisciplinaire qui saura vous faire rire et vous divertir avec ses anecdotes dans un feu roulant de comédie, de \"stepettes\" et de surprises. "
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventAttendanceMode": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventStatus": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/EventScheduled"
      }
    ]
  },
