        "@value": "Get ready for a sweet treat! The School of Atlantic Ballet proudly presents Roald Dahl's Willy Wonka JR. This enchanting musical brings the magic of Willy Wonka's chocolate factory to life with delightful songs from the classic 1971 film and a few fun new tunes.\r\nJoin Willy Wonka as he hides five golden tickets in his scrumptious candy bars, offering a free factory tour and a lifetime supply of candy to the lucky finders. While four of the winners are a handful, the kind-hearted Charlie Bucket and his grandfather embark on an unforgettable adventure. Will they navigate Wonka's whimsical world and follow the rules, or face the delicious consequences?\r\nDon’t miss this scrumdidilyumptious experience that promises to delight audiences of all ages! "
