    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Hert et Rhéal LeBlanc"
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Hert et Rhéal LeBlanc"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/inLanguage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": ""
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Come experience an Acadian party where you’re invited to sing, laugh, and dance to celebrate Hert LeBlanc’s 40-year career. Enjoy a memorable evening filled with the Acadian and country music that defined his 10 solo albums, as well as a few new songs from his upcoming project, set to be released in September 2026. Accompanied by his longtime partner, Rhéal LeBlanc, rediscover the chemistry and humour that define their relationship. Building on their individual successes as well as those with the group Les LeBlanc, celebrate and sing along with Hert and Rhéal LeBlanc.\r\nThe show is a DOUBLE FEATURE of musical performances showcasing the combined hits of artists Hert and Rhéal LeBlanc. Well-known to the public, this festive show is eagerly awaited by fans who have been following Hert for 40 years and Rhéal for nearly 15 years. "
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Venez vivre un party acadien vous invitant à chanter, rire et danser pour célébrer les 40 ans de carrière de Hert LeBlanc! Vivez une soirée mémorable au son de sa musique acadienne et country caractérisant ses 10 albums solo en carrière ainsi que quelques nouveautés de son nouveau projet à paraître en septembre 2026. Accompagné de son acolyte de toujours, Rhéal LeBlanc, retrouvez la complicité et l’humour qui caractérise leur relation. Forts de leur succès personnels ainsi qu’avec le groupe Les LeBlanc, fêtez et chantez avec Hert et Rhéal LeBlanc.\r\nLe spectacle se veut un DOUBLÉ de performances musicales des succès cumulées des artistes Hert et Rhéal LeBlanc. Bien connu du public, ce spectacle festif est attendu par les fans qui suivent Hert depuis 40 ans et Rhéal depuis près de 15 ans. "
      }
    ],
